name: Flu Clinic Finder
description: Application framework created to help users find flu clinics by location and open date/time. Conceived as a framework for other location- and time-based services.

name: SMC Service Finder
description: An expanded version of the flu clinic finder app, with selectable layers for various types of public services.

name: OpenN11
description:
Open-data directory of county services. Just the facts: who, what, where, when and when. 
Like calling 211. For any government service, not just human services.

name: CycleSMC - iOS
description: San Mateo County-specific version of Code for Philly's CyclePhilly iOS application to track cycling usage.

name: CycleSMC - Android
description: San Mateo County-specific version of Code for Philly's CyclePhilly Android application to track cycling usage.

name: OpenSMC Website
description: Starter website for OpenSMC.  Forked from sfbrigade.github.io, hosted on GitHub Pages.
